</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-138_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-139_ pf-text-1"><strong>Training</strong> - Regular first aid training and refresher courses for all employees, focusing on practical skills such as CPR and AED usage.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-141_ pf-text-1"><strong>Awareness campaigns</strong> - Conduct regular awareness campaigns within your organisation to highlight the importance of first aid readiness.

